			Escribir "Influencers recomendables"
			Escribir " + xxx (LucasArts, 1993)"
			Escribir " + xxx (Terminal Reality/3D Realms, 1995)"
			Escribir " + xx (Remedy/Apogee, 1996)"
		FinSi
